parse.retrosheet2.pbp.r:    from Marchi and Albert (2014), defines function
                            which allows automatic download of play-by-play
                            data from Retrosheet. Must run this function and
                            then move download.folder/unzipped/all2015.csv to
                            data/all2015.csv before running regression.R or
                            validation.r
regression.R:   code to produce results in Section 1 of paper
util.r:         utility function for estimating population variance
validation.r:   code to produce results in Sections 2 and 3 of paper
viz-rttm.r:     code to produce diagrams in slides
